-- Ken Lewis announces management changes at BofA
-- 
-- Mon Aug 3, 2009 1:39pm EDT
-- http://www.reuters.com/article/2009/08/03/us-brief-ken-lewis-announces-management-idUSTRE5724H120090803

 

 (Reuters) - Bank of America Corp: * Ken Lewis announces management changes at Bank of America * Says Sallie Krawcheck to run global wealth and investment management * Says Liam McGee, who has headed consumer and small business banking, has decided to leave * Says Brian Moynihan will become head of consumer banking * Says Tom Montag, who currently runs global markets, will also run global corporate and investment banking 

